name: JPGTO PATRONUM
description:
Pictured here, Mr. H teaching the freshmen their very first lesson of JPGTO PATRONUM; the most famous and one of the most powerful charms to create ‘The Perfect JPG’ known to the entire blockchain universe. 

This spell is extremely complex and difficult to master. In the past, it’s believed that only 2 out of 10 students at School of JPG succeeded in mastering it.
